Sally has 1 sister. Here's why:

The question states that "Her brothers have 2 sisters." This means that the group of people who are considered the siblings (brothers and sisters) to Sally, consists of herself, her two brothers, and her one other sister. 

Since we know Sally is part of this sibling group, she must be one of those two sisters mentioned in the question. Therefore, Sally has only 1 sister.
